channel.title: Looking For Project Partner!
channel.description: Title kinda says it all. I'm looking for a partner experienced in Java to help me run this and be my co owner and other programmer. I'm still learning java, but I got an excellent source to work with and it seems like it'll be loads of fun. I already got it up online, it's called Project Spirit. Just reply to this, or send me a pm.
